# Title: PowerShell Scripts Installed as Services
# Author: oscd.community, Natalia Shornikova
# Date: 2020-10-06
# Level: high
# Description: Detects powershell script installed as a Service
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.t1569.002
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/builtin/system/service_control_manager/win_system_powershell_script_installed_as_service.yml

EventID=7045 ImagePath IN ("*powershell*", "*pwsh*") Provider_Name="Service Control Manager"